# Text-based game simulation with rooms

[alphabet]
N S E W

[states]
Entrance
Kitchen
Hallway
Library
DiningRoom
Garden
Hell
Heaven

[initial_state]
Entrance

[accept_states]
Heaven

[transitions]
Entrance, W -> Hallway
Garden, N -> Heaven
Garden, S -> Hell
Hallway, W -> Library
Hallway, N -> Kitchen
Kitchen, W -> DiningRoom
DiningRoom, W -> Garden

[settings]
RemainInCurrentStateOnUndefinedTransition